{
  "stem": "21812.5",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I was in-- in the headquarters company, radio-- I was in headquarters company, battalion headquarters, 75th-- 290th Regiment, 75th Division, radio, Signal Division, and did my basic training there, and then was pulled out when the Army Specialized Training Program started, which was supposed to train.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They pulled out-- you had to pass all kinds of aptitude tests and took whole-day tests, different intelligence tests.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And if you passed, you went into a university.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There were three programs, engineering, medicine, and languages that they-- and if you-- if you graduated from that program, you became second lieutenant.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] So I passed, and knowing languages, they put me into engineering, of course, so I wound up at Iowa State and took the engineering courses and got quite a few college courses under my belt.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was lovely.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we were training to be officers.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then the Battle of the Bulge came upon the United States Army.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they felt they needed every available man.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They didn't know what was going to happen at that point.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So they stopped it, pulled everybody out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And now I was put into signals intelligence in Camp Crowder, Missouri.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And there [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] we-- I was training in signal intelligence.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then we were shipped to a-- I can't think of it now-- a unit outside of Washington in Virginia, which was a listening post.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And all for the-- by that time they were able to listen to all over the world, and also were teaching us Japanese code.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I learned Japanese code.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It was called katakana.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
